                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Balt<hi rend=\"sup\">o</hi></placeName>\n                                        <date>31st Mar 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My Dr Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your valued favor of the<lb/>\n                                        <date>29th</date> inst at hand yesterday was discussed<lb/>\n                                        at our Dinner Table, when <persName>Mrs C.\n                                                  Frances</persName>,<lb/> and\n                                                  <persName>Andrew</persName>\n                                        <del>wtre</del> were all gratified<lb/> to learn that you\n                                        enjoy'd at least<lb/> as good health as when here, all<lb/>\n                                        beg to reciprocate your good wishes<lb/> for many returns of\n                                        the approaching<lb/> holidays, hoping that ere another<lb/>\n                                        <date>Passover</date> shall come round, you will<lb/> be\n                                        able to introduce them to <persName>Mrs.\n                                        Leeser</persName>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I would 'twere in my power<lb/> to give you any\n                                        specific information<lb/> relative to the probability of a\n                                        vessel<lb/> sailing hence for\n                                                  <placeName>Kingston</placeName> after\n                                                  <add>פסח</add>,<lb/> in a general way those\n                                        vessels sail<lb/> without advertisement and without\n                                        notice<lb/> and if you <sic>enquire</sic> of the\n                                        consignees,<lb/> the general answer is, \"she is bound<lb/>\n                                        for the <placeName>W. Indies</placeName>\" I shall try\n                                        and<lb/> keep on the look out however,</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bn9xp44/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
