                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>and endeavor to inform you, meanwhile<lb/> however I would advise\n                                        you by all<lb/> means to write to <persName>Mr. Abm.\n                                                  Lazarus</persName><lb/> at <placeName>New\n                                                  York</placeName> (formerly of\n                                                  <placeName>Kingston</placeName>) who<lb/> would be\n                                        much more likely to procure<lb/> a passage from\n                                                  <placeName>New York</placeName>, and at<lb/> lower\n                                        rates too than from here<lb/> besides which he might\n                                        possibly<lb/> be of service to them otherwise<lb/> having a\n                                        vast family connexion<lb/> throughout the\n                                                  <placeName>Island</placeName>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Excuse haste and believe me</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours most Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">E. P. Cohen</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bn9xp44/canvas/p2"
                }
